platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 心ゆくまで疾走しよう！

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: We wouldn’t be surprised if Subway Surfers kept its spot near the top of the charts for decades to come. Its heart is the key to its stamina, revealed in loving details lavished on cities from Chicago to Shenzhen in its World Tours or in the lovable ruffians awarded in its frequent events. It’s a cinch to pick up, but we’re still finding new ways to master it years and miles later.
This blockbuster runner keeps charging ahead with loads of rewards to chase and special events set in cities across the world.
世界中の都市で楽しい特別イベントが随時開催。人気のランゲームを駆け抜け、報酬を集めましょう。
Ce célèbre jeu de course poursuit sa route avec de multiples récompenses à gagner et des événements qui se déroulent dans les villes du monde entier.
